{"type": "article", "id": 9129, "title": "Adidas Originals X PALACE 系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-04T07:53:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235230paGI9nlcM5Led7jW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t近日，Adidas Originals 和 英国滑板品牌 PALACE 再次联名推出新系列，并发布 Lookbook。去年两家的合作把街头滑板元素注入了 Adidas 服饰中，曾经得到过潮人们的热烈追捧，时隔 7 个月，他们的这次合作仍然以复古的服饰装备为主，突出数字，三叶草，三道杠等核心元素，同时，他们选择让PALACE 三角形图案在黑暗中发光。这个系列服饰从 5 月 2 日已经开始在部分品牌零售门店开售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235226UlzsSRiojhJVOP0f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235226sBC8xpQvVZ1IqRYy.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235227XLprvuwNqknBatFJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235227V8ieh7HlRLFuBAWz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235228Puypv43QYsJ6RcqB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235228NZzQm1IyguVMpfn3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235228gd2yW4jrxXtDHJEC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235229IGphmYBv8Eq0NPRy.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}